{"user":"Kite API rate limit hit ho gaya.","assistant":"Title: Kite API rate limit\\nWhat's happening: Too many requests too fast.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Wait 1 minute before retrying.\\n2) Reduce request frequency.\\n3) Batch orders if possible.\\n4) Rate limit: ~3 requests/second.\\nNote: App has built-in throttling but edge cases exist.\\nStatus: By design (Zerodha limit)"}
{"user":"Paper trading PnL real se match nahi kar raha.","assistant":"Title: Paper vs real PnL mismatch\\nWhat's happening: Execution differences.\\nReasons:\\n1) Slippage not simulated perfectly.\\n2) Real spreads vary.\\n3) Partial fills in real.\\n4) Market impact.\\nAdvice: Paper is indicative, not guaranteed.\\nStatus: Expected behavior"}
{"user":"Merge me duplicate timestamp error aa rahi.","assistant":"Title: Merge duplicate timestamp conflict\\nWhat's happening: Same timestamp exists in both datasets.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Merge dialog → Overlap Resolution setting.\\n2) Options: Keep-First, Keep-Last, Drop-Duplicates.\\n3) For most cases: Keep-Last (newer data priority).\\n4) Preview merge before confirming.\\nHypotheses: Overlapping date ranges in source files.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Merge fail ho gaya out of memory.","assistant":"Title: Merge out of memory\\nWhat's happening: Datasets too large for browser memory.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Reduce dataset sizes first.\\n2) Merge in smaller batches (2-3 at a time).\\n3) Close other browser tabs.\\n4) Use Chrome (better memory handling).\\nNote: Streaming merge handles up to ~500MB total.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Merge ke baad data range wrong dikha raha.","assistant":"Title: Wrong date range after merge\\nWhat's happening: Range calculation issue.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Check source datasets for timezone differences.\\n2) Ensure both use same UTC/IST setting.\\n3) Delete merged → re-merge with correct timezone.\\n4) Quality scan on merged dataset.\\nHypotheses: (1) timezone mismatch (2) source had gaps (3) sort issue.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Gap policy block kar diya merge ko.","assistant":"Title: Merge blocked by gap policy\\nWhat's happening: Gap policy set to 'Block' and gaps detected.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Merge dialog → Gap Policy change to 'Warn' or 'Allow'.\\n2) Or fix gaps in source datasets first.\\n3) For market holidays: Gaps are acceptable.\\n4) Re-attempt merge.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Merged dataset delete karne se source bhi delete ho jayega?","assistant":"Title: Merged dataset deletion\\nWhat's happening: Clarifying delete behavior.\\nAnswer: NO - Source datasets remain safe.\\nBut: If you checked 'Delete sources after merge' during merge → sources are already deleted.\\nRecovery: Backup restore or re-import.\\nTip: Keep sources until merged data verified.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Datasets merge me symbol mismatch.","assistant":"Title: Symbol mismatch in merge\\nWhat's happening: Different symbols cannot merge.\\nNext actions:\\n1) All datasets must have same symbol.\\n2) Check symbol assignment in Data Manager.\\n3) Edit symbol if incorrectly assigned.\\n4) Re-select and merge.\\nRule: Same symbol + same timeframe for merge.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Append vs Stitch merge mode me kya difference?","assistant":"Title: Append vs Stitch mode\\nWhat's happening: Two merge strategies.\\nAppend: Adds all rows from all sources, sorts by timestamp.\\nStitch: Connects end of one to start of next, no overlap allowed.\\nUse Append: When sources might overlap.\\nUse Stitch: For sequential data (2023 + 2024).\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Workspace invite accept nahi ho rahi.","assistant":"Title: Invite not accepting\\nWhat's happening: Invite link/token issue.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Check invite link not expired (7 days validity).\\n2) Login with exact email that received invite.\\n3) If expired → ask workspace owner to resend.\\n4) Clear cache → try accept link again.\\nHypotheses: (1) email mismatch (2) expired (3) already accepted.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Workspace me access denied aa raha.","assistant":"Title: Workspace access denied\\nWhat's happening: Permission issue.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Verify you're member of this workspace.\\n2) Check your role (Viewer can't edit).\\n3) Ask Admin/Owner to verify your permissions.\\n4) Try logout + login again.\\nRoles: Owner > Admin > Editor > Viewer.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Member invite kiya but unhe email nahi mila.","assistant":"Title: Invite email not received\\nWhat's happening: Email delivery issue.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Check spam/junk folder.\\n2) Verify email address spelled correctly.\\n3) Resend invite from Workspace Settings.\\n4) If still failing → share invite link manually.\\nNote: Some corporate emails block invites.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Workspace member role change kaise karu?","assistant":"Title: Change member role\\nWhat's happening: Update permissions.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Workspace Settings → Members tab.\\n2) Find member → Click role dropdown.\\n3) Select new role.\\n4) Save changes.\\nRequirement: You must be Admin or Owner.\\nNote: Cannot demote Owner.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Project workspace transfer kaise karu?","assistant":"Title: Transfer project\\nWhat's happening: Move project to different workspace.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Project Settings → General.\\n2) 'Transfer Workspace' option.\\n3) Select destination workspace.\\n4) Confirm transfer.\\nRequirement: Must be Owner + have access to target workspace.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Workspace delete karne se data bhi jayega?","assistant":"Title: Workspace deletion\\nWhat's happening: Clarifying impact.\\nAnswer: YES - All workspace data deleted.\\nIncludes: Projects, datasets, strategies, results.\\nBefore delete: Export/backup important data.\\nRecovery: Not possible after deletion.\\nStatus: Warning"}
{"user":"Viewer role wala kya kar sakta hai?","assistant":"Title: Viewer role permissions\\nWhat's happening: Read-only access.\\nCan do:\\n- View projects, datasets, strategies, results\\n- Export reports (if allowed)\\n- Access shared dashboards\\nCannot do:\\n- Create, edit, delete anything\\n- Invite members\\n- Change settings\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Workspace owner change kaise karu?","assistant":"Title: Change workspace owner\\nWhat's happening: Transfer ownership.\\nCurrent status: Not directly supported.\\nWorkaround:\\n1) Add new owner as Admin.\\n2) Transfer all projects to their workspace.\\n3) Delete old workspace.\\nFuture: Direct ownership transfer planned.\\nStatus: Workaround available"}
{"user":"Workspace storage quota exceed ho gaya.","assistant":"Title: Storage quota exceeded\\nWhat's happening: Workspace hit storage limit.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Data Manager → Delete unused datasets.\\n2) Clean old backtest results.\\n3) Remove duplicate strategies.\\n4) Check Cloud Dashboard for usage.\\nLimits: Based on plan (Free < Pro < Enterprise).\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Login ho gaya but workspace empty dikha raha.","assistant":"Title: Empty workspace after login\\nWhat's happening: Might be viewing wrong workspace.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Check workspace selector (top-left).\\n2) Switch to correct workspace.\\n3) If missing → check if invite accepted.\\n4) Contact workspace owner.\\nHypotheses: (1) wrong workspace (2) removed as member (3) invite pending.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Editor role wala member delete kar sakta hai?","assistant":"Title: Editor delete permissions\\nWhat's happening: Editors can delete their own created items.\\nCan delete: Own strategies, own datasets, own results.\\nCannot delete: Others' items, workspace itself.\\nFor full delete access: Need Admin role.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"RLS error aa raha database me.","assistant":"Title: RLS (Row Level Security) error\\nWhat's happening: Database permission denied.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Check you're logged in (auth required).\\n2) Refresh page to renew session.\\n3) Verify you own this data (user_id match).\\n4) Check Logs page for specific error.\\nHypotheses: (1) session expired (2) accessing other user's data (3) policy bug.\\nStatus: Troubleshooting"}
{"user":"Import progress stuck at 99%.","assistant":"Title: Import stuck at 99%\\nWhat's happening: Final processing step hanging.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Wait 2 minutes (large files need time).\\n2) Check browser console for errors (F12).\\n3) If frozen → Refresh page + re-import.\\n4) Try smaller file first.\\nHypotheses: (1) browser memory full (2) indexing slow (3) validation error.\\nStatus: Troubleshooting"}
{"user":"Strategy share karne ke baad edit nahi ho rahi.","assistant":"Title: Cannot edit shared strategy\\nWhat's happening: Sharing creates read-only copy.\\nClarification:\\n- Your original: Fully editable.\\n- Recipient's copy: Separate, they can edit their copy.\\nIf marketplace published: Cannot edit; create new version.\\nStatus: By design"}
{"user":"Batch backtest me ek fail ho gaya.","assistant":"Title: Batch backtest partial failure\\nWhat's happening: One or more runs failed in batch.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Batch Queue → Check failed run status.\\n2) Click to see error details.\\n3) Common issues: Data gap, strategy error, param invalid.\\n4) Fix issue → Retry failed only.\\nOther runs unaffected.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Authentication session expire ho gayi.","assistant":"Title: Session expired\\nWhat's happening: Login token timed out.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Refresh page → auto re-auth may work.\\n2) If not → Click Login again.\\n3) 'Remember me' keeps session longer.\\nSession duration: ~1 hour idle, 7 days active.\\nStatus: By design"}
{"user":"Email verification link expired.","assistant":"Title: Verification link expired\\nWhat's happening: Email links valid for 24 hours.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Login page → 'Resend verification'.\\n2) Check email (spam folder too).\\n3) Use new link within 24 hours.\\n4) If issues persist → Contact support.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Password reset link kaam nahi kar raha.","assistant":"Title: Password reset link not working\\nWhat's happening: Link expired or used.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Reset links valid for 1 hour.\\n2) Request new reset from login page.\\n3) Use link immediately.\\n4) Check you're on correct site URL.\\nHypotheses: (1) expired (2) already used (3) wrong browser.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
{"user":"Data import me timezone galat ho gayi.","assistant":"Title: Wrong timezone in import\\nWhat's happening: Timestamps shifted incorrectly.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Delete imported dataset.\\n2) Re-import → Timezone dropdown in wizard.\\n3) Select correct zone (IST = UTC+5:30).\\n4) Preview timestamps before confirming.\\nNote: App stores as UTC internally.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
