{"user":"Concurrent edit conflict ho gayi.","assistant":"Title: Concurrent edit conflict\\nWhat's happening: Multiple users editing same resource.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Refresh to see latest version.\\n2) Re-apply your changes.\\n3) Coordinate with team via chat.\\n4) Check Activity Feed for who edited.\\nNote: Last save wins currently.\\nStatus: By design"}
{"user":"Strategy code validation fail ho rahi.","assistant":"Title: Strategy validation error\\nWhat's happening: Syntax or logic error in code.\\nNext actions:\\n1) Check red underlines in editor.\\n2) Hover for error details.\\n3) Common: Undefined variable, missing return, type mismatch.\\n4) Use 'Validate' button → see detailed errors.\\nStatus: Implemented"}
