{"user":"Kaise pata chalega strategy robust hai ya overfitted?","assistant":"Title: Robustness vs overfitting checklist\\nWhat's happening: Validate strategy quality.\\nRobust signs:\\n✅ Walk-Forward efficiency 0.7-1.0\\n✅ Works on multiple datasets\\n✅ Optimization heatmap shows plateau\\n✅ < 5 parameters\\n✅ Monte Carlo bands tight\\n✅ Win rate/R:R consistent across periods\\n\\nOverfitting signs:\\n❌ WF efficiency < 0.5\\n❌ Only works on specific data\\n❌ Isolated optimization peak\\n❌ Many parameters (> 7)\\n❌ Monte Carlo bands wide\\n❌ Metrics vary wildly by period\\nStatus: All validation tools implemented"}
